some questions about I.D.s.

163
00:09:36,254 --> 00:09:38,004
I'm sorry. You're a what?

164
00:09:38,119 --> 00:09:40,927
- I'm a private investigator.
- How old are you?

165
00:09:41,061 --> 00:09:42,100
I'm 19.

166
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:45,716
So, can you tell me
how student I.D.s work?

167
00:09:46,305 --> 00:09:48,421
Oh, well, exactly like debit cards.

168
00:09:48,517 --> 00:09:50,555
Each term, students can
add money to their account

169
00:09:50,671 --> 00:09:52,728
