the names on the cards were aliases?

196
00:11:20,827 --> 00:11:25,819
"Niels Bohr, Sylvia Plath,
Leonardo Fibonacci, Honus Wagner"?

197
00:11:25,915 --> 00:11:28,413
Just because I didn't go
to a school with a water polo team

198
