a $1,000 card for 100 bucks.

221
00:12:34,106 --> 00:12:35,775
- And so you paid him?
- Yeah.

222
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:38,524
He asked for a fake name, and...
told me to meet him the next day

223
00:12:38,621 --> 00:12:41,006
