227
00:12:50,128 --> 00:12:53,993
And believe me,
I hated turning in that janitor guy.

228
00:12:54,397 --> 00:12:57,125
I'm sure he's got kids
to feed or something.

229
00:13:26,075 --> 00:13:27,113
Excuse me,

